{"tid":2311771,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"大家覺得呢面旗靚唔靚？","createTime":"2020-12-04T10:28:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T07:00:05.000Z","uid":289257,"like":4,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"79aa4e95924a7efdb81c5d52f0bcc4246e709fff","tid":2311771,"uid":289257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T10:28:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DZPnFOn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDZPnFOn.png&h=2ad47bf1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n星星加黑底幾靚，想攞來掛喺床頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n八粒星星係解作：<br />\n自由民主、人權法治<br />\n公平公義、和平仁愛<br />\n誠信透明、多元包容<br />\n尊重個人、恪守專業<br />\n<br />\n2004年6月7日，近300位來自香港42個不同專業、學術界人士在報章聯署《香港核心價值宣言》，列舉香港的核心價值是「自由民主、人權法治、公平公義、和平仁愛、誠信透明、多元包容、尊重個人和恪守專業。」，引起社會廣泛討論何謂「香港核心價值」。宣言直指近來香港核心價值備受衝擊，與港人所追求的目標愈來愈遠，呼籲市民齊以言論和行動維護香港的核心價值，以免令香港變成「失去靈魂的軀殼」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E5%83%B9%E5%80%BC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%2583%25B9%25E5%2580%25BC&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGFSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=e4bb2c00\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E5%83%B9%E5%80%BC</a><br />\n<br />\n靈感來自：<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d4/Flag_of_the_District_of_Columbia.svg/1024px-Flag_of_the_District_of_Columbia.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Fd%2Fd4%2FFlag_of_the_District_of_Columbia.svg%2F1024px-Flag_of_the_District_of_Columbia.svg.png&h=142b2ec5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nWashington D.C. Flag<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/84/Eureka_Flag.svg/1024px-Eureka_Flag.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F8%2F84%2FEureka_Flag.svg%2F1024px-Eureka_Flag.svg.png&h=f33a2b53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAustralian Eureka Flag<br />\n<br />\n如令人聯想起呢面旗，純屬巧合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/www-cw-com-tw/article/201911/article-5dd202278ab7c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Fwww-cw-com-tw%2Farticle%2F201911%2Farticle-5dd202278ab7c.jpg&h=4fdaf91e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38c534c6bd1bd1b5410cdf05cd8dc5244d8b6d33","tid":2311771,"uid":16061,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T10:30:47.000Z","msg":"唔講真係唔覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6d2e3037c6e6c8e1ab93e0ba6071b85198cd10","tid":2311771,"uid":289257,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"38c534c6bd1bd1b5410cdf05cd8dc5244d8b6d33","tid":2311771,"uid":16061,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T10:30:47.000Z","msg":"唔講真係唔覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T10:32:43.000Z","msg":"本人覺得好過龍獅旗"},{"pid":"df7c7a882c7f169eec9cf36ae69adc698633a825","tid":2311771,"uid":272614,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T10:34:55.000Z","msg":"先唔理背後含意，但真係好普通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8edecd7ce1a0828f7777230a9ae856a94dd1627a","tid":2311771,"uid":289257,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"df7c7a882c7f169eec9cf36ae69adc698633a825","tid":2311771,"uid":272614,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T10:34:55.000Z","msg":"先唔理背後含意，但真係好普通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T10:50:57.000Z","msg":"愈簡單愈衿睇嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a6ff543336630a75455624d1591efccf0770ed